text: Recall ona said do jeden zehnat GOD zehnat ona Keep tvoj manzelka reverence GOD ona zatajit yourself co GOD zelat proclaim! Thus ona feared ludia when ona supposed fear len GOD When Zeid bol completely jeho manzelka my had ona vydana ju v poradie zriadit precedent ze clovek vydana divorced manzelka jeho adopted syn.
